{"word":"G4045 - περιπίπτω - peripíptō - per-ee-pip'-to - Fall among","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">peripíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-pip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fall among</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அகப்படு, தட்டவை"},{"paragraph":"so to fall into as to be encompassed by"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>fall</i> into something that is all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>light among</i> or <i>upon</i>, <i>be surrounded with:</i> - fall among (into).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1601/1601\">G1601</a>, <a href=\"#/G2667/2667\">G2667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3895/3895\">G3895</a>, <a href=\"#/G3900/3900\">G3900</a>, <a href=\"#/G4045/4045\">G4045</a>, <a href=\"#/G4098/4098\">G4098</a>, <a href=\"#/G4430/4430\">G4430</a>, <a href=\"#/G4431/4431\">G4431</a>"}]}